snippet.title: Knights of the Silver Table - Trailer 2021
snippet.description:
Knights of the Silver Table is a new action packed 2D Action RPG coming soon to Steam PC.

Update on Knights of the Silver Table - June 2021: https://cenokga.com/development-update-on-knights-of-the-silver-table-june-2021

Steam Page at:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1057040/Knights_of_the_Silver_Table

Stay updated at:

Website - https://cenokga.com
Twitter - https://twitter.com/Cenokga
Facebook - https://facebook.com/Cenokga
Instagram - https://instagram.com/Cenokga

The intended Audience for this Channel.

Although games by Cenokga are family friendly, the intended audience for games by Cenokga are persons over the age of 13.

If you are under the age of 13, Do not use this website or Channel.
Person's found to be verifiable under the age of 13 will be reported to YouTube.

Cenokga does not knowingly collect or store information on children under 13 on it's database.

If Cenokga has collected any information about users under the age of 13, that info will be deleted as soon as possible.

Cenokga Ltd. Co., it's Owner, Affiliates or Partners take no responsibility in determining if Third Parties used by Cenokga are compliant with COPPA.

If a Third Party used by Cenokga is violating COPPA rules, Cenokga will cease use of that Third Party as soon as possible or require that they delete the information of children under 13 that they have collected on Cenokga's behalf without Cenokga's knowledge.
